creator: Erik Melkersson
descriptionHtml:
An massive multi-player online ant controlling game using your real location from GPS.

Several Species of ants compete for control of the ground. You join one of them and help them spread and dominate.

You will be founding colonies, help them expand and breed, defend against other animals and enemies. When the colonies have grown big enough you may attack enemy colonies too. Cooperate with your allies, help them and coordinate attacks.

NOTE: You need a valid android device. (No rooting or other modifications)

Demo video:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ur6xWmftM3A
descriptionShort: Ant controlling game using real location. Help one species expand and dominate.
